## Process Improvement Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define the process to improve and its current performance
- [ ] 2. Map the current process step-by-step
- [ ] 3. Identify waste: unnecessary steps, handoffs, delays, rework
- [ ] 4. Design an improved process
- [ ] 5. Implement the change with the team
- [ ] 6. Measure improvement and iterate

## Key Inputs
- Process: {{process}}
- Current Pain Points: {{current_pain_points}}
- Performance Data: {{performance_data}}
- Improvement Goal: {{improvement_goal}}
